# Licence Authority secrets — the PRIVATE signing key + issued-licence registry
# must NEVER be committed or shipped in the client app (build prompt §2.1, §9).
.licence_keys/
*.private.pem
licence_registry.json
# Issued client licences are delivered out-of-band, not committed.
clients/*.lic
# The active deployment licence is environment state (issue one per install).
/licence.lic
